  [Website color schemes](https://hookagency.com/website-color-schemes/) matter more than most businesses realize.
  
  Your colors do more than make things “pretty.” They influence trust, readability, engagement, and even conversions – before a visitor reads a single sentence. In fact, unattractive design causes a significant portion of visitors to lose interest fast.
  
  In this updated 2026 version, we’re rounding up **fresh palettes, trend insights, and practical tips** so you can choose colors that feel intentional, current, and right for your audience.
  
  You’ll find:
  
  - Real-world palette examples
  - New 2026 color schemes and moodboards
  - What’s trending in digital color design right now
  - How to use color strategically on your site
  
  ![YouTube video](https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lhNCOHEI-nE/hqdefault.jpg)
  
