  The crazy part is that color scheme matters way more than you think – and a cohesive and eye-catching color scheme is one of the top aspects of [web design](https://hookagency.com/website-design/) that will make your website MORE ATTRACTIVE + BEAUTIFULLY DESIGNED (Step one – Step Two = [Get more traffic Search Engine Optimization](https://hookagency.com/roofing-marketing/seo/).)
  
  38 percent of visitors will stop engaging with a website if the content or layout is unattractive. (Blue Corona – a [home services marketing agency](https://hookagency.com/)) Given 15 minutes to consume content, two-thirds of people would rather read something beautifully designed than something plain. (Source: Adobe, [Social Media Color](https://www.lockedownseo.com/social-media-colors/))
  
