  ## 7 New Color Schemes for 2024
  
  Taking some more inspiration from fashion and painting company color trends, we’ve curated 7 additional color schemes that are sure to be popular throughout the new year. This year, bright colors and jewel tones are highlighted, as well as a few prominent muted shades (one of them taking the cake as “Color of the Year”). Be sure to draw inspiration from any of these color schemes, and it will definitely help to [smarten up](https://hookagency.com/blog/who-is-the-smartest-person-in-the-world/), and level up whatever web design project you’re taking on next.
  
  ### **1\. Electric Blue – [Cleo](https://www.awwwards.com/sites/cleo-1) Website Color Scheme**
  
  ![electric blue color scheme](https://hookagency.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/electric-blue.png)
  
  ![Pantone NYFW Spring/Summer 2022 Color Report](https://hookagency.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/pantone-nyfw-2022.png)
  
  ###### Source: [WWD.com](https://wwd.com/eye/lifestyle/pantone-unveils-fashion-color-trend-report-for-nyfw-spring-1234908577/)
  
  The color scheme of this money app website almost perfectly reflects some of the colors included in [Pantone’s Fashion Color Trend Report for NYFW Spring](https://wwd.com/eye/lifestyle/pantone-unveils-fashion-color-trend-report-for-nyfw-spring-1234908577/). In both fashion and web design color trends, you can expect to see plenty of traditional shades (like this classic blue), but also bright and bolder tones that add a sense of revitalization to whatever color scheme they are included in.
  
  **Electric Blue:** #373e98
  
  **Hot Pink:** #f16775
  
  **Shocking Yellow:** #fee36e
  
  **Chartreuse-ish:** #ceb92c
  
  **Darkest Gray:** #2a2a2a
  
  ### **2\. Hot Orange – [Bonjour Paris](https://www.awwwards.com/sites/bonjour-paris) Website Color Scheme**
  
  ![hot orange color scheme](https://hookagency.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/hot-orange.png)
  
  ![hot orange fashion color trend](https://hookagency.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/orange.jpeg)
  
  ###### Source: [Stylecaster.com](https://stylecaster.com/color-trends-2022/\#:~:text=Luckily%2C%20the%20color%20trends%20for,all%20bright%20as%20can%20be.&text=Just%20look%20at%20the%20color,with%20its%20own%20special%20tang.)
  
  It seems like one of the “It” colors on the runways of this upcoming year may be this orange shade. So, we’re back with another grayscale palette that includes a bright pop of color, that color being hot orange. This website design shows that bright colors can still come across as luxurious and high-end when used correctly.
  
  **Black:** #000000
  
  **Medium Gray:** #565656
  
  **Light Gray:** #9e9e9e
  
  **Hot Orange:** #fba92c
  
  **White:** #FFFFFF
  
  ### **3\. Muted Green – [The Cool Hunter](https://www.awwwards.com/sites/the-cool-hunter-shop) Website Color Scheme**
  
  ![muted green color scheme](https://hookagency.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/muted-green.png)
  
  ![color of the year paint trend](https://hookagency.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/evergreen-fog.jpeg)
  
  ###### Source: [Sherwin-Williams.com](https://www.sherwin-williams.com/homeowners/color/find-and-explore-colors/paint-colors-by-family/SW9130-evergreen-fog)
  
  [Better Homes and Gardens](https://www.bhg.com/decorating/color/paint/2022-color-of-the-year/) curated a list of every “2022 Color of the Year” announced thus far by painting companies. By far, some variation of this muted green color seems to be the most popular shade. This e-commerce website incorporates this popular shade in a very simple way using a background image, showing that your website design doesn’t necessarily have to be overly complicated to look cohesive and professional, especially when using the right colors.
  
  **Beige:** #c8b7a6
  
  **Perriwinkle:** #7d94b5
  
  **Dusty Rose:** #c29591
  
  **Maroon Brown:** #703f37
  
  **Muted Green:** #b6c199
  
  ### **4\. Lemon Lime – [VerticalLoop](https://www.awwwards.com/sites/verticalloop-design-for-good) Website Color Scheme**
  
  ![lemon lime color scheme](https://hookagency.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lemon-lime.png)
  
  The citrus-y color scheme gives off a fresh and vibrant feel, and it definitely works to make this web design more exciting, even though the layout is quite simple.
  
  **Light Lime:** #abd699
  
  **Fresh Lemon:** #ffe26a
  
  **Teal:** #75c9b7
  
  **Mint:** #c7ddcc
  
  **Navy:** #16123f
  
  ### **5\. Jewel Tones – [Regent5](https://99designs.com/profiles/aneley/designs/1226162) Website Color Scheme**
  
  ![jewel tones color scheme](https://hookagency.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/jewel-tones.png)
  
  ![pantone fashion color trend](https://hookagency.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/pantone-fashion-color-trend.jpeg)
  
  ###### Source: [Pantone.com](https://www.pantone.com/articles/fashion-color-trend-report/new-york-fashion-week-spring-summer-2022)
  
  Another major color trend is the use of jewel tones, and they are great to include in web designs. [Pantone’s Spring/Summer 2022](https://www.pantone.com/articles/fashion-color-trend-report/new-york-fashion-week-spring-summer-2022) color report highlights plenty of dynamic jewel tones that give off an expensive vibe. This Regent5 website design also has an expensive feel, communicated by the deep blues and purples incorporated throughout the site.
  
  **Mauve:** #A96762
  
  **Deep Blue:**#2F5C8F
  
  **Mandarin:** #d85c27
  
  **Lavender:** #b999be
  
  **Night Moon:** #14365d
  
  ### **6\. Sorbet – [Mamma Mia](https://www.awwwards.com/sites/mamma-mia-italian-gourmet) Website Color Scheme**
  
  ![sorbet color scheme](https://hookagency.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/sorbet.png)
  
  ![spring 2022 trending colors](https://hookagency.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/spring-2022-colors.webp)
  
  ###### Source: [Fashionista.com](https://fashionista.com/2020/05/spring-2022-color-trends)
  
  The popular colors in our post-COVID society are ones that [energize and uplift](https://fashionista.com/2020/05/spring-2022-color-trends). After the past couple of years of isolation, people want to wear and see shades are soothing and invigorating at the same time. This website color scheme does a great job of including natural/organic shades that are exciting at the same time.
  
  **Creme:** #f4d8ae
  
  **Tangerine:**#dc7027
  
  **Pistachio:** #b6c48e
  
  **Peachy:** #ea8a81
  
  **Black Cherry:** #301008
  
  ### **7\. Orchid – [Gong](https://www.awwwards.com/sites/gong) Website Color Scheme**
  
  ![orchid color scheme](https://hookagency.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/orchid.png)
  
  This [Orchid shade](https://fashionista.com/2020/05/spring-2022-color-trends) is another one that is going to be popular in both fashion and web design. This color scheme is heavily influenced by technology trends and mobile apps that are already prominent in our society like Spotify and Lyft. This just goes to show the influence that technology tends to have on our preferences, especially post-COVID.
  
  > “Orchid flower has an intense, hyper-real and energizing quality that will stand out in both real life and digital settings,” – [Joanne Thomas, Head of Content for Coloro](https://fashionista.com/2020/05/spring-2022-color-trends)
  
